{"id":315432,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/09/维权网-陈信滔：警匪杀人抢劫炮制冤狱瓜分民营/","date":"2013-09-27T00:34:06Z","modified":"2013-09-27T00:34:06Z","title":"维权网 | 陈信滔：警匪杀人抢劫炮制冤狱瓜分民营资产，民告官13年久拖不决","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"><span> </span></p>\n<div><span> </span><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a><br /><span> </span></p>\n<div><span>我叫陈信滔是福建省福州市的一名军队转业干部，响应国家号召下海经商创业，不幸遭警匪设局酿惊天惨案。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>13</span></span><span>年来历经</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>5</span></span><span>任市政法委书记、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>4</span></span><span>任市公安局长、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>3</span></span><span>任市中院院长，辩护律师从</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>60</span></span><span>多岁一直辩到近</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>80</span></span><span>岁</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>&#8230;&#8230;.</span></span><span>无法审结！</span></div>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<div><span>惊</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span><span>  </span></span></span><span>天</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span><span>  </span></span></span><span>巨</span><span> </span><span>案</span></div>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>2001</span></span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>2</span></span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>20</span></span><span>日，福建省福州市发生了一起骇人听闻的警匪勾结杀人抢劫案。警匪为谋财害命、垄断旧车交易市场。设置圈套滥用三级公安机关和数十名武装刑警动用冲锋枪、手枪，将手无寸铁的平民诱入设伏点，仅距</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>3-5</span></span><span>米从背后扫射</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>150</span></span><span>多发子弹，击中</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>47</span></span><span>发残忍枪杀，将枪、钱撒在死者身边，伪造持枪抢劫、拒捕被击毙的“现场”（死者殁年仅</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>32</span></span><span>岁）。并调动警用拖车，洗劫我</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>31</span></span><span>部小汽车等财物达</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>500</span></span><span>多万，警匪坐地分赃，我因外出侥幸逃过死劫。</span></div>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<div><span>我从部队转业经商才</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>4</span></span><span>年，不仅巨额财产被抢（股东投资、转业安置费、贷款、亲朋借款等），依法到公安机关报案，却被构陷入狱长达</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>3</span></span><span>年。此案还骗取打黑除恶首战大功，十几名警察不仅立功受奖而且升官发财。</span></div>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<div><span>警匪酿就惨绝人寰的惊天惨案，丧尽天良、天怨神怒。经公安部挂牌督办案情真相大白。</span></div>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>2004</span></span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>3</span></span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>1</span></span><span>日，历经</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>8</span></span><span>次退回补充侦查；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>3</span></span><span>次变更起诉罪名，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>2</span></span><span>次被判有罪又</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>2</span></span><span>次发回重审，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>1</span></span><span>次撤诉重又起诉，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>9</span></span><span>次开庭审理的司法奇闻，饱尝</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>3</span></span><span>年冤狱苦难才被当庭宣判无罪释放。刚</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>40</span></span><span>多岁的我已满头白发、病痛缠身。</span></div>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>2006</span></span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>5</span></span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>16</span></span><span>日，福州市中级人民法院判处首恶徐承平死刑；判处原福州市公安局晋安分局岳峰刑警中队长郑军死刑；判处原福州市公安局晋安分局刑警大队长刘雄（全国优秀人民警察、福州市十佳警察）死刑缓期两年执行。</span></div>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>2007</span></span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>6</span></span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>20</span></span><span>日，福建省高院终审裁定维持原判；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>2009</span></span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>4</span></span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>21</span></span><span>日，经最高法院核准执行死刑。</span></div>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<div><span>官</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span><span>    </span></span></span><span>官</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span><span>   </span></span></span><span>相</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span><span>   </span></span></span><span>护</span></div>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>2005</span></span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>8 </span></span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>5</span></span><span>日，我向福州市中院提起民事索赔被裁定不予受理。</span></div>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>2006</span></span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>6</span></span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>30</span></span><span>日，应松年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>, </span></span><span>姜明安</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>, </span></span><span>毕玉谦</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>, </span></span><span>尹田</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>, </span></span><span>杨立新</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>, </span></span><span>张新宝等</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>6</span></span><span>位法学专家，在京专题进行研讨后一致认为：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span><span>   </span></span></span></div>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<div><span>福州市公安局是职务侵权。参与本案的干警的行为是职务行为，适用民法通则第</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>121</span></span><span>条关于职务侵权的规定，应承担连带赔偿责任。</span></div>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>2006</span></span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>7</span></span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>15</span></span><span>日，我正式向福建省高院提起民事财产索赔立案，时至</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>2008</span></span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>12</span></span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>9</span></span><span>日，历经</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>2</span></span><span>年多省高院以诉讼标的额低为籍口，推诿到福州市中院受理。</span></div>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<div><span>历经</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>7</span></span><span>年漫长的上访、信访、控告，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>2011</span></span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>4</span></span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>20</span></span><span>日，福州市中院才勉强立案。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>2012</span></span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>3</span></span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>27</span></span><span>日，不出预料全面驳回我的诉求。</span></div>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<div><span>上诉至福建省高院又经历一年多，于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>2013</span></span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>4</span></span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>7</span></span><span>日，福建省高院栽定</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>:</span></span><span>指令福州市中院对本案进行重新审理，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>9</span></span><span>年又兜回原地。</span></div>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>2013</span></span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>6</span></span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>27</span></span><span>日，福州市中级法院决定重新开庭审理本案。</span></div>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>2013</span></span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>6</span></span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>25</span></span><span>日，因顾忌网络舆情突然宣布延期开庭至今…</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>.</span></span></div>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<div><span>寻</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span><span>    </span></span></span><span>求</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span><span>   </span></span></span><span>公</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span><span>   </span></span></span><span>道</span></div>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<div><span>这桩骇人听闻警匪勾结案，涉案的警察上至公安局长下到一般民警，有名姓可查就达</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>39</span></span><span>人；市、区、派出所，刑警、巡警、交警联动；十余名警察开枪杀人，更出具了书面的伪证炮制冤狱，并参与抢劫、瓜分我的巨额财产。替罪羊的仅是冲在前台小爪牙，哪些领导者、组织者、杀人者、获利者、伪证者毫发未损，或升官发财，或异地为官、或叛逃美国。而受害者</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>13</span></span><span>年来深陷苦难的深渊，乞求国家法律维护公平正义而不能。</span><span></span></div>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<div><span>面对如此伤天害理严重践踏人权的恶性案件，采取的是拖、赖、推、扯皮的流氓做法，对我正当的上访维权采取的是盯梢、监听、断网、拘传、绑架、构陷……！</span></div>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<div><span>恳请为彰显人间公平正义伸出援手！</span><span></span></div>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<div><span>链接：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span> 1</span></span><span>、警匪勾结案真相大白</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>http://review.jcrb.com/zyw/jfgj/<span>      </span></span></span></div>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>2</span></span><span>、我向警方索赔</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>1300</span></span><span>万被驳回</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>http://fj.qq.com/a/20120331/000206.htm</span></span></div>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>3</span></span><span>、福州警匪无间道</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>http://t.cn/ao1EvI</span></span><span>（视频）</span></div>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span> </span></span></div>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span> </span></span></div>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span> </span></span></div>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<div><span>转业军官：陈信滔</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span><span>  </span></span></span><span>敬礼！</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>13609554166 </span></span><span>（案情材料备索）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span><span>  </span></span></span></div>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span> </span></span></div>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span> </span></span></div>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>2013</span></span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>9</span></span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>24</span></span><span>日</span></div>\n<p><span> </span></div>\n</div>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=b4fd4ae247\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/mstlf\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18270,18269,20534],"tags":[16910]}